Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look. On our island, we use shells to coin money. These Shell-Coins circulate as money. {この島では貝を使って貨幣カインが使われているんです - not sure what's kain}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange to use shells as money, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're so pretty...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see it at least once though. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Me'd like to see it too. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:11.36,Sign,,0,0,100,,{\bord5\blur7\c&HCEC2BD&\3c&H660073&\3a&H1F&}Episode 79 \N{\fs60}Reconciling is Hard! {仲直りって大変!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen it? \NThe Worlds of Love yesterday. { そこほれ・ザ・ワールド in manga - no clue what's this sokohore, would assume some parody of existing TV show}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! How could we have not seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one interesting issue, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful and lovely idea, \Nto use shells as money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish I could also go there \Nand bring back at least one of those coins. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they called it Shell-Coins, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a Shell-Coin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get it, Korekiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to that island last summer \Nto spend my vacation there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been holding on to this since then. {/brought back}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Korekiyo.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It brings back so many memories \Nof that everlasting summer paradise. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just recollecting it now sends my heart fluttering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long? \NDon't you know time and tide wait for no man?{Time is of the essence}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... Well... Thank you, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive! That's a real Shell-Coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much prettier than what we saw on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Korekiyo. Lend me this for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is an important memento. \NIf it gets destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Show it, Korekiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my bad! It almost felt \Nlike I forced you to do something just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's real pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Please handle it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme see it too! Hey! I wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it. {/enoguh}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't be so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a chance to look at it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shell-Coin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Korekiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do this?! \NIt was my precious memento!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I apologized, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you destroyed it \Nout of jealousy, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you still after me \Neven though I apologized? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your game, \Ndestroying others' precious possessions?! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo, you shouldn't be fuming so much over it.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, they said this thing would cost \Nabout 1000 yen in normal Japanese money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about I bring 1000 yen tomorrow \Nand we forget about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that nonsense! \NReturn it back to me in its original state!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There, see? Stick it on cellotape\Nand it's back to how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never accept this kind of hack job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, ain't you a nitpicking type, Korekiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to hang out \Nwith someone who's constantly complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a monster, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't talk like that, Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you getting cocky, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Please do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's are white too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not the time to be talking in riddles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some magic item \Nfor restoring broken things back to how they were!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,An item that can restore broken things to how they were?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! As expected \Nof the Great Magician Taruruuto-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, damn... Even Taru's magic is of no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! What are you gonna do about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't avoid the question!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Adieu, Ryoguchiya Korekiyo! {/farewell}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! That's cowardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have any shame at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I'll never forgive him, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody likes guys like him! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious Shell-Coin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo seems awfully mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:08:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've no magic item for\Nrestoring broken things to their original state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Me - dropout magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru! Let's go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Me still sleepy. \NLet me sleep, Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, you'll be late, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakey-wakey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're so troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... This isn't getting anywhere...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Korekiyo is still mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sup, Korekiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Restore my Shell-Coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, 1000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be such a sourpuss.{/cold}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, accept this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna hear any of that!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't compare my precious Shell-Coin \Nto such earthly things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What did {\i1}I{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as Korekiyo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so insensitive, Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In one ear and out the other - \Nit's like talking to a horse. {preaching to the deaf; chanting the nembutsu into a horse's ear​ ... anything we say is of no use}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To a horse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you ignore it, it'll go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? A drop? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hey, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, you're drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you need to be \Nsuch a pain in the ass, Korekiyo? {lit: anyway irritating me}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I even offered to compensate you justly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Right, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of us sure are fond of sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop sleeping all the time \Nand do something already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have an item to fix what's broken, \Njust some item for placating someone, or anything, would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A nice morning to you, Taru-kun!{/Congratulations on awakening}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This doesn't look like Taru's living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it feels like a portal to another world.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Sister Ria is looking so hot again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{homehome fuhe hahoho *** - dont think its supposed to mean anything}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go, Rookanga-kun! {ru-kangakun}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanga, kanga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He just hit Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of thing is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't even beat him, \Nyou won't ever get the items you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruru Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do, Taru.{/sloppy}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you wanted \Nthat item by any means?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how Ria is giving him private tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that Taru can still get \Nnew magical items even while he's in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When I died and went to a magical land,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because we needed Jump to Heaven, \Nwe had to duel other magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to get stamps from them \Nand exchange those for magical items.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I don't know \Nwhat item it is that you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Giving up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, you're light years away \Nfrom the item you want.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Me not down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Me beat this guy. Beat and stamp him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Will get the magical item Return-to-how-it-walrus. {motodoorikun - no clue what's the joke}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With Return-to-how-it-walrus, \Nreturn the seashell to how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru and Korekiyo will reconcile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru is doing that for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To make Korekiyo and I reconcile...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Me win and get a stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Me do my best for Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You work so hard for me, \Ninstead of sleeping at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he's sleeping all day long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, I'll reconcile with Korekiyo \Nusing my own strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo, please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be some way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? I'm ready to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I said no, it means no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo-sama, hey! \NPretty please, rub-rub.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're saying you wish to go that far...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Will you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,First, get on your knees and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Just as I thought, \Nyou weren't really gonna apologize, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your answer, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm the one who needs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Korekiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast. It's nowhere near enough \Nfor me to forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rub my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done with that, \Ncarry me on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And hand me that gum eraser.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And do the school lunch duty instead of me. {being responsible for school lunch distribution and clean-up​}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning duty as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we continue tomorrow, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning already, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me can't give up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Me'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Me won't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruru Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender, kanga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go faster, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo, can I ride it next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, have at it. Come on! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need me to forgive you or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Me'll win and stamp him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do my best for Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru is doing his best for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to do it too!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold fast, Korekiyo!{/lets go}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Clatter-clatter!{g, assumed sound that horse hooves makes}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Korekiyo taking it a little too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, lick my foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you give me that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you'd do anything \Nto earn my forgiveness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you wanna go that far, Ryoguchiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't interfere. \NThis is between me and Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If your remorse is that deep, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Condemn the offense, but not the offender. {condemn the offense, but not the offender; detest the sin, but weep for the sinner​}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let bygones be bygones.{to forgive and forget; to let bygones be bygones; to sweep under the carpet; to wipe the slate clean}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when mended together with cellotape, \NShell-Coin is still Shell-Coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's smile will forever \Nremain unbroken in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Return-to-how-it-walrus-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You put broken thing in this cage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and it'll return to how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! \NWe'll return it to how it was, Korekiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mended!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mended, everyone! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Korekiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of the great Magician Taruruuto-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem! Leave that up to me! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Except my magic wears off in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shell-Coin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you tricked me \Ninto rejoicing prematurely...{lit: gave a premature joy; short-lived elation}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? \NDidn't you say you'd forgive me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru and Korekiyo quarrel again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a dropout.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Need to train more.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause you do nothing but annoy people, \Nalways pulling trouble out of your ass! {g}
